trans-unit.target: A pipeline with <embeddedLabel>Azure ML Batch Scoring Activity</embeddedLabel>.

trans-unit.source: The following sample pipeline containing an <embeddedLabel>AzureMLBatchScoring</embeddedLabel> Activity gets the location of the input file from your input tables, invoke the Azure Machine Learning batch scoring API, and copy the batch scoring output to the blob specified in your output table definition.
trans-unit.target: The following sample pipeline containing an <embeddedLabel>AzureMLBatchScoring</embeddedLabel> Activity gets the location of the input file from your input tables, invoke the Azure Machine Learning batch scoring API, and copy the batch scoring output to the blob specified in your output table definition.

trans-unit.source: An AzureMLBatchScoring Activity can have only one input and one output table.
trans-unit.target: An AzureMLBatchScoring Activity can have only one input and one output table.
